snippet.title: Zeta Fighters Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Download Zeta Fighters from: www.zetafighters.com/downloadnow

Zeta Fighters is a new kind of competitive mobile game. It combines elements from MOBAs and cave shooters to an intense cross-platform touchscreen experience for iOS and Android.

Play against other players in real-time & rise through the ranks and win intensive space battles. Unlock awesome special weapons and choose your ultimate combination. You are to become the Master of the Universe! 

Zeta Fighters is now available in Finland, Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Germany. Join the Battle!
